of the Dragon to its proper glory.

530
00:50:17.692 --> 00:50:18.943
King Viserys: Of course.

531
00:50:19.026 --> 00:50:21.779
It's not my daughter
you lust for. is it?

532
00:50:22.613 --> 00:50:25.616
It's my throne.

533
00:50:26.534 --> 00:50:29.036
Go back to the Vale. Daemon.

534
00:50:29.120 --> 00:50:31.998
to your lawful wife.

535
00:50:32.081 --> 00:50:36.961
Strive to restore whatever
scrap of honor remains in you.

536
00:50:37.044 --> 00:50:40.548
Or don't. Matters not to me.

537
00:50:40.631 --> 00:50:43.050
As long as you are gone
from my sight for good.

538
00:50:43.134 --> 00:50:44.177
♪ ♪

539
00:50:46.971 --> 00:50:50.433
- (sheathes knife)
- (exhales)

540
00:50:50.516 --> 00:50:52.351
As you wish. brother.

541
00:50:55.396 --> 00:50:58.441
(door closes)

542
00:51:06.574 --> 00:51:08.618
(birds cawing)

543
00:51:21.672 --> 00:51:24.300
Have you spoken to her?

544
00:51:26.928 --> 00:51:29.972
No.

545
00:51:33.142 --> 00:51:35.895
It is not in Rhaenyra's
nature to be deceitful.

546
00:51:37.063 --> 00:51:38.583
I cannot say the
same for your brother.

547
00:51:40.024 --> 00:51:41.400
You believe he lied?

548
00:51:42.652 --> 00:51:44.862
How often does he
speak the pure truth?

549
00:51:45.947 --> 00:51:49.033
How does confessing
to such things serve him?

550
00:51:52.078 --> 00:51:55.122
By reducing you.

551
00:51:57.208 --> 00:51:58.835
(King Viserys sighs)

552
00:51:59.961 --> 00:52:04.382
Whatever transpired.
Rhaenyra is not innocent.

553
00:52:04.465 --> 00:52:07.009
Only because Daemon
tried to corrupt her.

554
00:52:07.093 --> 00:52:10.263
Daemon and Rhaenyra
share the blood of the dragon.

555
00:52:10.346 --> 00:52:12.056
They are restless and chaotic.

556
00:52:12.139 --> 00:52:14.100
She swore to me that
she remains a maiden.

557
00:52:15.810 --> 00:52:18.145
And I believe her.

558
00:52:19.105 --> 00:52:20.147
♪ ♪

559
00:52:46.924 --> 00:52:49.969
(sighs)

560
00:53:22.501 --> 00:53:23.961
King Viserys: That dagger

561
00:53:24.045 --> 00:53:25.485
once belonged to
Aegon the Conqueror.

562
00:53:27.757 --> 00:53:29.634
It was Aenar's before that.

563
00:53:30.593 --> 00:53:32.803
And before that...

564
00:53:32.887 --> 00:53:35.014
well. it is difficult to know.

565
00:53:40.603 --> 00:53:44.690
Before Aegon's death. the
last of the Valyrian pyromancers

566
00:53:44.774 --> 00:53:46.192
hid his song in the steel.

567
00:53:53.074 --> 00:53:56.619
Rhaenyra: "From my blood...

568
00:53:56.702 --> 00:53:59.997
"come the Prince
That Was Promised...

569
00:54:02.083 --> 00:54:05.586
and his will be the
Song of Ice and Fire."

570
00:54:10.091 --> 00:54:13.511
The responsibility I
have handed to you.

571
00:54:13.594 --> 00:54:15.763
the burden of this knowledge...

572
00:54:17.056 --> 00:54:20.518
it is larger than
the throne. the king.

573
00:54:20.601 --> 00:54:22.061
It is larger than you

574
00:54:22.144 --> 00:54:24.188
and your desires.

575
00:54:28.943 --> 00:54:31.404
Jaehaerys would've
disinherited you.

576
00:54:31.487 --> 00:54:32.571
For a lie?

577
00:54:34.073 --> 00:54:36.701
You've yet to ask me for
the truth of what happened.

578
00:54:36.784 --> 00:54:39.328
The truth does not
matter. Rhaenyra.

579
00:54:39.412 --> 00:54:41.205
Only perception.

580
00:54:41.288 --> 00:54:42.206
You have exposed yourself.

581
00:54:42.289 --> 00:54:45.626
Now we must both
suffer the consequences.

582
00:54:45.710 --> 00:54:49.630
Were I born a man. I could
bed whomever I wanted.

583
00:54:49.714 --> 00:54:51.257
I could father a dozen bastards.

584
00:54:51.340 --> 00:54:53.259
and no one in your
court would blink an eye.

585
00:54:53.342 --> 00:54:57.555
You are right... but
you were born a woman.

586
00:54:57.638 --> 00:55:01.225
So you'll strip me of my titles
and name Aegon in my stead.

587
00:55:01.308 --> 00:55:03.394
I would.

588
00:55:03.477 --> 00:55:05.855
But it is mine to hold
the realm together.

589
00:55:05.938 --> 00:55:07.648
not sow it with
further division.

590
00:55:09.525 --> 00:55:12.069
Your courtship is at an end.

591
00:55:12.153 --> 00:55:14.405
You will wed Ser
Laenor Velaryon.

592
00:55:14.488 --> 00:55:16.866
and you will do
so without protest.

593
00:55:17.575 --> 00:55:19.952
The son of the Sea Snake.

594
00:55:20.036 --> 00:55:22.538
So I can be a remedy for
your political headaches.

595
00:55:22.621 --> 00:55:25.332
You are my political headache!

596
00:55:29.712 --> 00:55:31.964
Your wedding to
Ser Laenor Velaryon

597
00:55:32.048 --> 00:55:34.759
will unite the two most
powerful houses in the realm.

598
00:55:34.842 --> 00:55:39.055
With the combined strength of
our shared dragons and naval fleets.

599
00:55:39.138 --> 00:55:40.765
no one would dare
to stand against us.

600
00:55:40.848 --> 00:55:42.224
The House of the Dragon

601
00:55:42.308 --> 00:55:45.686
will stand as one for
a further generation.

602
00:55:45.770 --> 00:55:47.205
And what will you
do about the vulture

603
00:55:47.229 --> 00:55:49.940
who perches upon your throne?

604
00:55:50.024 --> 00:55:51.358
What vulture?

605
00:55:52.026 --> 00:55:54.862
Your Hand.

606
00:55:54.945 --> 00:55:59.158
Otto Hightower has served
two kings loyally and faithfully.

607
00:56:00.242 --> 00:56:02.912
He wants Aegon to be named heir.

608
00:56:02.995 --> 00:56:05.498
And he will stop at
nothing to see it done.

609
00:56:05.581 --> 00:56:08.584
Including spying on me
to bring about my ruin.

610
00:56:09.502 --> 00:56:12.588
You speak of The
Conqueror's vision

611
00:56:12.671 --> 00:56:15.132
and the need for strength
and unity across the realm.

612
00:56:15.216 --> 00:56:17.635
But how can that be accomplished

613
00:56:17.718 --> 00:56:19.488
with your most trusted
adviser so self-interested?

614
00:56:19.512 --> 00:56:21.972
Every lord and lady that
calls for an audience with me.

615
00:56:22.056 --> 00:56:24.767
every man on my small council.

616
00:56:24.850 --> 00:56:27.895
and all councils past.
has been self-interested.

617
00:56:27.978 --> 00:56:30.356
- It is unavoidable.
- I disagree.

618
00:56:30.439 --> 00:56:32.942
I will do my duty as heir

619
00:56:33.025 --> 00:56:34.610
and wed Ser Laenor.

620
00:56:37.029 --> 00:56:39.698
But you must first
do yours as king.

621
00:56:50.126 --> 00:56:52.253
- (door closes)
- Your Grace.

622
00:56:54.880 --> 00:56:56.173
Five days.

623
00:56:59.510 --> 00:57:01.345
I'm sorry. Your Grace?

624
00:57:01.428 --> 00:57:03.931
King Viserys: Though
it was some time ago.

625
00:57:04.014 --> 00:57:07.852
The details... they
fade in memory.

626
00:57:07.935 --> 00:57:11.355
My father was a hale and
healthy warrior and dragonrider

627
00:57:11.438 --> 00:57:13.190
at the peak of his abilities.

628
00:57:13.274 --> 00:57:15.860
Jaehaerys named
a great royal hunt

629
00:57:15.943 --> 00:57:18.237
to celebrate him being
named the Hand of the King.

630
00:57:19.446 --> 00:57:23.951
Five days later my...
my father lay dead.

631
00:57:25.786 --> 00:57:27.288
Tourneys last longer.

632
00:57:28.122 --> 00:57:31.250
Baelon the Brave.

633
00:57:31.333 --> 00:57:33.419
rider of Vhagar.

634
00:57:33.502 --> 00:57:35.379
heir to the Iron Throne...

635
00:57:36.046 --> 00:57:38.883
dead of a burst belly.

636
00:57:40.926 --> 00:57:43.387
The gods have a dark wit.

637
00:57:43.470 --> 00:57:44.513
It was a grim day.

638
00:57:46.640 --> 00:57:49.310
- I recall it all too well.
- Yeah...

639
00:57:50.186 --> 00:57:52.313
It was a good day for you.

640
00:57:53.564 --> 00:57:56.275
Jaehaerys named you
Hand in Baelon's stead.

641
00:57:59.486 --> 00:58:02.448
That's hardly how I
viewed it. Your Grace.

642
00:58:03.449 --> 00:58:05.034
It was a duty.

643
00:58:07.745 --> 00:58:11.498
You served my grandsire
nobly in his final days.

644
00:58:12.958 --> 00:58:15.294
You are the man that
taught me how to be King.

645
00:58:17.213 --> 00:58:21.258
- Oh. you honor me. Your Grace.
- (King Viserys sighs)

646
00:58:21.342 --> 00:58:22.927
Just five days...

647
00:58:24.637 --> 00:58:28.015
you went from being another
man in Jaehaerys's court.

648
00:58:28.098 --> 00:58:30.142
to the second most
powerful man in the realm.

649
00:58:31.435 --> 00:58:32.478
I wonder...

650
00:58:34.021 --> 00:58:36.815
how long did it take you to
choose yourself over your King?

651
00:58:39.026 --> 00:58:41.070
Your Grace?

652
00:58:42.363 --> 00:58:44.865
I will never recover
from Aemma's death.

653
00:58:45.366 --> 00:58:47.993
But Alicent...

654
00:58:48.077 --> 00:58:50.079
she took me through
the worst of my grief.

655
00:58:52.539 --> 00:58:55.167
She was a calculated
distraction.

656
00:58:56.293 --> 00:58:59.588
I only now realize
how well-calculated it was.

657
00:58:59.672 --> 00:59:02.633
That is an absurdity.

658
00:59:02.716 --> 00:59:04.551
The Queen loves you...

659
00:59:06.011 --> 00:59:07.846
as I know you love her.

660
00:59:07.930 --> 00:59:10.516
Your interests no longer align
with those of the realm.

661
00:59:10.599 --> 00:59:13.852
Your judgment has
been compromised.

662
00:59:13.936 --> 00:59:16.480
A loyal Hand must tell his king

663
00:59:16.563 --> 00:59:19.650
a discomforting truth
from time to time. Your Grace.

664
00:59:19.733 --> 00:59:21.360
If he doesn't...

665
00:59:22.736 --> 00:59:24.655
he's failed as a servant.

666
00:59:25.739 --> 00:59:28.158
You were a faithful
servant. Otto.

667
00:59:37.835 --> 00:59:39.545
The crown and the realm

668
00:59:39.628 --> 00:59:42.589
both owe you a debt
that can never be repaid.

669
00:59:43.882 --> 00:59:46.427
But I can no longer
trust your judgment.

670
00:59:46.510 --> 00:59:49.179
(sorrowful music playing)

671
01:00:07.781 --> 01:00:09.366
(knocks on door)

672
01:00:10.034 --> 01:00:11.994
Come.

673
01:00:16.790 --> 01:00:19.752
I hope you can forgive
the late hour. Princess.

674
01:00:24.631 --> 01:00:27.593
I took great care
in its preparation.

675
01:00:30.471 --> 01:00:33.265
If not brewed properly.
it can either prove ineffective

676
01:00:33.349 --> 01:00:35.225
or else bear

677
01:00:35.309 --> 01:00:37.478
- unpleasant...
- Brewed properly?

678
01:00:39.146 --> 01:00:40.814
I'm sorry. what is that?

679
01:00:41.648 --> 01:00:42.691
A tea. Princess.

680
01:00:44.318 --> 01:00:46.862
From the King.

681
01:00:46.945 --> 01:00:52.117
It will rid you of any
unwanted consequences.

682
01:00:52.201 --> 01:00:54.453
♪ ♪

683
01:00:58.165 --> 01:00:59.792
(door opens)

684
01:01:03.504 --> 01:01:05.089
(door closes)

685
01:01:13.055 --> 01:01:15.849
♪ ♪

686
01:01:35.452 --> 01:01:37.037
(vocalizing)

687
01:02:01.103 --> 01:02:03.147
♪ ♪

687
01:02:04.305 --> 01:03:04.220
Do you want subtitles for any video?
